Class UvcContext

    Finalizable

    public class UvcContext
extends NativeObject
    UvcContext is the Java manifestation of a native uvc_context_t, together with some additional Java-level state that should be maintained throughout a UVC session.

        Constant Field Values

      • cameraManagerImpl

        protected CameraManagerImpl cameraManagerImpl
        We hold on to a CameraManagerImpl, but we DON'T ref count it. All we're trying to do is keep same from being GC'd so long as we are alive; this will keep the instance management in ClassFactoryImpl.getCameraManager() working better. To wit: whenever the UvcDeviceManager ultimately gets GC'd and finalized, we'll be release()d and all will be well.
